menu "Zenbedded RCL Configuration"

    config ZENBEDDED_RCL_ENABLE
        bool "Enable Zenbedded RCL"
        default y
        help
          This option enables the Zenbedded Ros Client Library (RCL).

    config ZENBEDDED_RCL_THREAD_PRIORITY
        int "Zenbedded thread priority"
        default 5
        help
            Zephyr thread priority for the zenbedded thread.
            Lower number = higher priority.

    config ZENBEDDED_RCL_THREAD_STACK_SIZE
        int "zenbedded thread stack size (bytes)"
        default 2048
        range 1024 16384
        help
            Stack size for the zenbedded thread.
endmenu
